1
00:00:36,700 --> 00:00:42,060
=Twin Fire Dawn=

2
00:00:42,100 --> 00:00:45,060
=Episode 19=

3
00:00:49,860 --> 00:00:50,820
(Shaoyuan.)

4
00:00:51,660 --> 00:00:52,620
(Shaoyuan.)

5
00:01:03,020 --> 00:01:04,100
(Shaoyuan.)

6
00:01:05,100 --> 00:01:08,580
(I can't stay by your side any longer.)

7
00:01:08,900 --> 00:01:09,619
Cheng Yi.

8
00:01:09,620 --> 00:01:10,500
Cheng Yi!

9
00:01:14,300 --> 00:01:15,100
What's wrong?

10
00:01:17,780 --> 00:01:18,940
I dreamed about Cheng Yi.

11
00:01:20,140 --> 00:01:21,340
He was saying goodbye to me.

12
00:01:24,800 --> 00:01:26,699
Do you think something
might've happened to Cheng Yi

13
00:01:26,700 --> 00:01:27,900
while he was chasing Gu Nianchi?

14
00:01:29,500 --> 00:01:30,940
Dreams are usually the opposite.

15
00:01:31,060 --> 00:01:32,100
Don't worry too much.

16
00:01:39,700 --> 00:01:41,900
After my father passed away,

17
00:01:42,100 --> 00:01:44,460
we moved around a lot
before settling in Cheng Yi's village.

18
00:01:44,940 --> 00:01:46,780
At that time, his parents had just died,

19
00:01:47,980 --> 00:01:49,620
so my mother took him in.

20
00:01:51,940 --> 00:01:53,500
He called my mother his godmother,

21
00:01:55,020 --> 00:01:57,100
and I've always treated him
like my own younger brother.

22
00:01:58,460 --> 00:02:00,220
When Gu Nianchi burned down the village,

23
00:02:02,060 --> 00:02:03,300
Cheng Yi survived too

24
00:02:03,340 --> 00:02:05,420
because he had gone out looking for me.

25
00:02:06,660 --> 00:02:07,659
Then that means

26
00:02:07,660 --> 00:02:09,340
he's someone blessed with good fortune.

27
00:02:09,740 --> 00:02:11,180
So don't worry.

28
00:02:11,540 --> 00:02:12,180
How about this?

29
00:02:12,260 --> 00:02:13,299
Tomorrow morning,

30
00:02:13,300 --> 00:02:14,900
I'll go look for him with you.

31
00:02:14,980 --> 00:02:16,220
He'll be fine.

32
00:02:16,780 --> 00:02:17,780
Get some rest.

33
00:02:41,100 --> 00:02:42,100
Let's sleep.

34
00:02:56,180 --> 00:02:58,140
Do you know
where the military seal is now?

35
00:02:58,940 --> 00:03:00,180
Gu Shaoyan.

36
00:03:01,740 --> 00:03:03,820
I'd rather die than tell you.

37
00:03:10,300 --> 00:03:11,780
Gu Shaoyan.

38
00:03:12,940 --> 00:03:14,700
You've committed countless evil deeds.

39
00:03:15,380 --> 00:03:17,620
Your hands are stained
with so many lives.

40
00:03:18,580 --> 00:03:20,300
You'll go to hell for this.

41
00:03:21,340 --> 00:03:23,740
Shaoyuan will avenge me.

42
00:03:24,740 --> 00:03:25,940
Just you wait.

43
00:03:36,780 --> 00:03:37,740
Little brother.

44
00:03:42,460 --> 00:03:43,820
Your tie is crooked.

45
00:03:52,300 --> 00:03:53,620
You...

46
00:03:54,100 --> 00:03:56,820
Why don't you
take better care of yourself?

47
00:03:58,500 --> 00:04:00,420
I really don't want to kill people.

48
00:04:00,700 --> 00:04:03,380
But every time, you force me into it.

49
00:04:24,260 --> 00:04:25,580
Don't be upset.

50
00:04:26,020 --> 00:04:27,140
Isn't she just a girl?

51
00:04:27,980 --> 00:04:28,540
Come on.

52
00:04:32,700 --> 00:04:35,620
I earned some money today.
I'll take you out for a drink.

53
00:04:36,300 --> 00:04:36,900
Here.

54
00:04:37,420 --> 00:04:37,940
Okay.

55
00:04:40,020 --> 00:04:40,740
Remember this.

56
00:04:40,900 --> 00:04:42,100
No matter what happens,

57
00:04:42,540 --> 00:04:43,860
I will always stand by your side.

58
00:04:46,380 --> 00:04:47,860
(I'll always be your younger brother.)

59
00:04:48,500 --> 00:04:49,980
(And you'll always be my big brother.)

60
00:04:55,340 --> 00:04:57,339
At least I've done something

61
00:04:57,340 --> 00:04:58,620
for Shaoyuan's happiness.

62
00:05:01,940 --> 00:05:02,620
Godmother,

63
00:05:03,340 --> 00:05:04,700
you can rest easy now too.

64
00:05:05,300 --> 00:05:06,860
Shaoyuan doesn't just have me anymore.

65
00:05:07,060 --> 00:05:08,180
He has a wife now too.

66
00:05:09,300 --> 00:05:10,799
Things will only get better from now on.

67
00:05:12,380 --> 00:05:13,620
What are you talking about?

68
00:05:14,020 --> 00:05:15,700
You'll always be my younger brother.

69
00:05:16,220 --> 00:05:17,860
Got it.

70
00:05:18,380 --> 00:05:19,020
Yi.

71
00:05:20,180 --> 00:05:20,980
What is it?

72
00:05:21,660 --> 00:05:22,540
Be careful on the way.

73
00:05:22,900 --> 00:05:23,700
Come back early.

74
00:05:24,740 --> 00:05:25,980
Got it.

75
00:05:26,100 --> 00:05:28,020
I'm not a child anymore.

76
00:05:28,400 --> 00:05:30,720
No matter how old you get,
you'll always be my younger brother.

77
00:05:40,980 --> 00:05:41,660
Commander.

78
00:05:41,780 --> 00:05:43,740
If he won't tell us
where the military seal is,

79
00:05:44,140 --> 00:05:46,320
how are we supposed
to take back the position of Commander?

80
00:05:46,320 --> 00:05:48,600
Do you think he'll still talk
after being tortured like this?

81
00:05:53,460 --> 00:05:54,580
It's fine.

82
00:05:55,980 --> 00:05:57,620
I still have another way.

83
00:06:09,860 --> 00:06:10,900
Take care of him.

84
00:06:11,580 --> 00:06:12,500
Yes, Commander.

85
00:06:52,460 --> 00:06:53,180
Miss Xue.

86
00:06:56,180 --> 00:06:57,180
Could you help me?

87
00:06:58,780 --> 00:06:59,780
Lieutenant Li isn't here,

88
00:07:01,580 --> 00:07:02,460
and it's really

89
00:07:03,180 --> 00:07:04,660
inconvenient for me alone.

90
00:07:55,820 --> 00:07:56,740
Sorry.

91
00:07:56,860 --> 00:07:58,180
Did I hurt you?

92
00:08:23,940 --> 00:08:24,659
All done.

93
00:08:24,660 --> 00:08:26,020
Then I'll be leaving now.

94
00:08:32,100 --> 00:08:33,300
Will you stay with me?

95
00:08:36,060 --> 00:08:38,940
You want me to stay with you?

96
00:08:40,660 --> 00:08:42,300
You refused to marry me before.

97
00:08:43,540 --> 00:08:45,100
And now that I'm like this,

98
00:08:46,300 --> 00:08:47,620
I can't give you anything anymore.

99
00:08:49,900 --> 00:08:50,980
Not fame,

100
00:08:53,260 --> 00:08:54,060
or status.

101
00:08:54,420 --> 00:08:56,540
Do you think those
are the only things I care about?

102
00:08:57,000 --> 00:08:58,320
I've studied abroad for many years.

103
00:08:58,320 --> 00:09:00,580
What I learned there
was to bravely pursue what I truly want.

104
00:09:01,460 --> 00:09:02,580
Back then,

105
00:09:03,020 --> 00:09:04,420
I had someone marry in my place

106
00:09:05,260 --> 00:09:06,339
because I refused to accept

107
00:09:06,340 --> 00:09:08,700
a love and marriage arranged for me.

108
00:09:18,020 --> 00:09:20,300
The moment I met you on the street,

109
00:09:21,260 --> 00:09:22,540
I realized

110
00:09:24,340 --> 00:09:25,860
I'd already fallen for you.

111
00:09:28,660 --> 00:09:30,580
And when I found out
you were the Commander,

112
00:09:30,620 --> 00:09:31,899
I admired you even more

113
00:09:31,900 --> 00:09:33,500
for everything you've done for Yancheng.

114
00:09:35,020 --> 00:09:36,900
I thought we were
going to miss our chance.

115
00:09:37,260 --> 00:09:39,060
My heart was filled with mixed emotions.

116
00:09:40,620 --> 00:09:41,819
I never expected

117
00:09:41,820 --> 00:09:43,180
that even now, we still could...

118
00:09:50,580 --> 00:09:55,270
♪How can broken love ever go on?♪

119
00:09:56,580 --> 00:10:01,900
♪How much hope must fade into despair?♪

120
00:10:02,400 --> 00:10:05,980
♪In the blink of an eye,
everything falls apart♪

121
00:10:06,320 --> 00:10:09,330
♪Bound by the fate we cannot escape♪

122
00:10:09,500 --> 00:10:14,620
♪You and I caught in
this tangled love and hate♪

123
00:10:15,740 --> 00:10:20,930
♪Fragile hearts can hardly bear goodbye♪

124
00:10:21,990 --> 00:10:27,590
♪How many times
must pain cut deep before we wake?♪

125
00:10:28,130 --> 00:10:31,510
♪I once gave myself
to you so completely♪

126
00:10:31,760 --> 00:10:34,709
♪Still holding on to that heart♪

127
00:10:34,710 --> 00:10:39,849
♪Only to suffer your fatal blow♪

128
00:10:39,850 --> 00:10:44,169
♪How desperately
I long to hold you close♪

129
00:10:44,170 --> 00:10:46,749
♪Yet I approach you with such caution♪

130
00:10:46,750 --> 00:10:49,029
♪How could a stand in ever have♪

131
00:10:49,030 --> 00:10:52,579
♪The right to be loved by you?♪

132
00:10:52,580 --> 00:10:57,109
♪If love is nothing
more than endless schemes♪

133
00:10:57,110 --> 00:10:59,640
♪Used and abandoned in the end♪

134
00:10:59,780 --> 00:11:01,729
♪Still I walk into♪

135
00:11:01,730 --> 00:11:05,329
♪The trap you set without regret♪

136
00:11:05,330 --> 00:11:09,379
♪How desperately
I long to hold you close♪

137
00:11:09,380 --> 00:11:11,959
♪Yet keep it buried deep inside♪

138
00:11:11,960 --> 00:11:14,119
♪A stand in can never cross♪

139
00:11:14,120 --> 00:11:17,559
♪The shortest distance between us♪

140
00:11:17,560 --> 00:11:22,530
♪If love can
make someone lose themselves♪

141
00:11:22,690 --> 00:11:27,360
♪Then let me stay by your side♪

142
00:11:30,140 --> 00:11:31,709
♪A substitute♪

143
00:11:31,710 --> 00:11:36,710
♪Needs no reason♪

